==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Atomization
<hw>At`om*i*za"tion</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act of
reducing to atoms, or very minute particles; or the state of being so
reduced.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>The reduction of fluids into fine
spray.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Atomize</ent>⟦br⟧
